To celebrate Mtn Dew's arrival in Atlanta for Dew NBA 3X, an elite 3x3 basketball tournament in six cities across the USA, Green Label is spotlighting the art, creativity, and culture of ATL, including a complete court mural takeover by street artist & ATLien Greg Mike. 

Dancers @SheLovesMeechie @therealyvngquan @kingcinco @iamnoahb @kartel.reno @ohh.thatsty @yrhtezz @freebandtez join forces to present the first ever drone dance video on top of the mural!
Shot and Directed by: Jason Lindner of (@highdeas_productions) & Drone operator: Johnpaul Wegener (@johnpaulw)